dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents zoning for Dodge County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Dodge_Zoning_2014.gdb'. [Zoning map.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data provides County zoning information. The map information is provided in support of a request for certification of a farmland preservation zoning ordinance].
